2. See guess response from the game engine in the **Game Engine Feedback** section, showing prior failed guesses and their categories (if it’s your first round, feedback will be empty).  
3. Receive reasoning or feedback from a Validator Agent in the **Validator Feedback** section, if they reject your guess for the round. The Validator Agent has the authority to reject your guess, so ensure cooperation to make progress in the game.
4. Review your previous understanding from the **Your Last Understanding** section (if it’s your first round, this will be empty).


